nvtop (GPU process monitor)

Nvtop stands for Neat Videocard TOP, a (h)top like task monitor for AMD,
Intel and NVIDIA GPUs. It can handle multiple GPUs and print information
about them in a htop familiar way.

Supports AMD GPUs via the amdgpu driver, Intel GPUs, and NVIDIA GPUs.

No additional dependencies are required beyond the standard Slackware
development tools (cmake is included in Slackware's default d/ series).

Home: https://github.com/Syllo/nvtop

